data.description:
Nicely maintained 3 bedr 1 1/2 bath split level home in the village of Carthage. Owners reluctantly need to relocate, so someone new will get to enjoy this comfortable home. Property boasts an ample yard with a newly fenced in area  and a natural partially wooded section in the back. Comes with a conveniently attached 1 car garage, plus a detached 2 car garage with extra room for a work bench and /or storage. Spacious deck on the rear of the house with easy access from the dining /kitchen area, or from the yard, with room for barbecuing, outdoor dining or just relaxing. Beautiful hardwood floors grace the majority of the home except for kitchen, baths and tiled entry room. Partially finished lower level provides option for 3rd bedroom or office/den. The 1/2 bath on this level could easily be expanded to include a tub/shower. Plenty of storage space in the laundry/utility room. Owners recently installed metal roofing on both house and garage, plus new vinyl flooring in main bath. Home is  
 in great condition, ready to move in and is  convenient to all the features the village of Carthage provides. Call today for your private showing.
